Package visuals.gameModes.easy

Class FXEasyController

java.lang.Object
visuals.gameModes.FXAbstractGameController
visuals.gameModes.easy.FXEasyController
All Implemented Interfaces:
Initializable, FXIGameController
public class FXEasyController extends FXAbstractGameController implements Initializable, FXIGameController
A controller class that manages the gameplay for the easy level in a memory match game. Extends FXAbstractGameController and implements Initializable and FXIGameController.
